   <body>
      <section>
         <p>The following table provides a brief description of all the Deal Manager System
         Properties. Go to <uicontrol>Setup</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol>Custom Settings</uicontrol>
         &gt; click <uicontrol>Manage</uicontrol> next to Deal Manager System Properties.</p>
         <p>
            <table>
               <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="col1"/>
                  <colspec colname="col2"/>
                  <thead>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Setting</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Description</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Deal Guidance Callback Class</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>The deal guidance callback class name. The class should implement the <i>CustomClass.IDealGuidanceCallback</i> interface.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Deal Optimizer Callback Class</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>The deal optimizer callback class name. The class should implement the <i>CustomClass.IDealOptimizerCallback</i> interface.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Display Dimensions In Guidance</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Enable this setting to display rule dimensions in the pricing guidance detail.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Display Net Price Per Unit In Guidance</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Enable this setting to display the net price per unit in the pricing guidance detail.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Hide Percentile Range In Guidance</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Enable this setting to hide the percentile range in the pricing guidance detail. You can hide either percentile range or price range, not both.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Hide Price Range In Guidance</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Enable this setting to hide the price range in the pricing guidance detail. You can hide either percentile range or price range, not both.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p>
